Comment: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------EDJP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.53,0:21:37.54,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\fs16}I must be dreaming tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:43.28,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\fs16}We erase it from our memories
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:49.97,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\fs16}You can't escape I only know this secret with you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:57.33,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\fs16}「I'll believe」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.77,0:22:08.49,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}あなたを照らした光彩がわたしの記憶にも在るなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.62,0:22:19.13,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}全てを証明していこう存在していく為の理由を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.63,0:22:29.05,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}人間は誰も忘れていく痛めた傷跡も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.36,0:22:35.95,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}時の流れ見送る度に薄れる感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.09,0:22:41.38,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}たけどこれ以上見過ごしたくなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.95,0:22:45.78,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}time over　消えていく残像それは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.84,0:22:50.80,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}あなたそのものだから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.97,0:22:54.35,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I can't live life without you by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.35,0:22:57.73,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}「I'll believe」孤独も因縁さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.87,0:23:01.30,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}灼熱の記録の欠片
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.31,0:23:04.51,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}未来を映すbrightness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.51,0:23:11.20,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}あなたを照らした光彩がわたしの記憶にも在るから
